Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait compared to the duration of Accepted + Wait - User within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + Resolved in variants that do not include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time between Accepted + In Progress and Accepted + Wait in cases that later execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Average cycle time of Accepted + Wait when it appears after Queued + Awaiting Assignment and before Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants where Completed + In Call is absent versus variants where it is present
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Time elapsed from the start of the case to the completion of Accepted + Wait in processes ending with Completed + Closed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time it takes to complete Accepted + Wait after Accepted + In Progress in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Total duration of Accepted + Wait in variants that transition directly to Completed + Resolved without intermediate waiting states
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time between Accepted + Wait and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress, specifically in traces containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum cycle time of Accepted + Wait when preceded by Accepted + Assigned and followed by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + Closed in variants that include exactly one instance of Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait relative to Accepted + Wait - Implementation in cases managed by the same resource group (e.g., V30 or C9)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
